commit message:
Removed local.properties and added to gitignore. Otherwise one gets build errors. As the build.xml states:

The local.properties file is created and updated by the 'android' tool.
It contains the path to the SDK. It should *NOT* be checked into
Version Control Systems.

Merge pull request #8 from dicer/master

Removed local.properties and added to gitignore.

Tweak AP groupings for position estimate, fix some log typos.

Signed-off-by: Tod Fitch <Tod@FitchDesign.com>
